
{center}
{subhead} Bill McEwen gone!{def}{p}
{left}
{p} {p}

Following Jim Collas, public relations manager has left Amiga with the
message "I did not leave Amiga, Amiga left me."
{p} {p}
Following this, all details of Amiga's personel in the USA have been
removed from the www.amiga.com [.de] website.
{p} {p}
Tom Schmidt maintains in his Executive Updates that Amiga is still
on track.
{p} {p}
23/9/99 : In a recent confidential email from Bill McEwen to a limited
group of people, including AIO he has again stated ;
{p} {p}
"I will say this, I did not leave Amiga, Gateway told me to leave"
{p} {p}
Expect the rest of the email to publicly known when Bill McEwen decides.